content.text: Then things began to change. I think it was shortly after he encouraged Margaux to see 'Sarah' on the phone to me that I noticed the beginning. And then, while his friends were willing to either go limitlessly chase him or take warning to the Almighty, Jeffrey began to get that look in his eye. He was marking his territory, sometimes I think anyone else I think could. I always hoped he wasn't spurred to action by my silence. We don't care - let's get rid of all prying eyes.
